OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1772201047
OL,3,CParents of baby boy who lived two days
OL,4,Csay maternity review must lead to
OL,5,Cchange
OL,7,FThe parents of a baby boy who lived
OL,8,Ffor just two days have said a national
OL,9,Fmaternity review must lead to
OL,10,Faccountability - not be "bullet points
OL,11,Fin a report" looked back on in the
OL,12,Ffuture.
OL,14,FApril will mark four years since
OL,15,FPreeti and Rishi Joshi's son Ansh died.
OL,17,FThe couple had planned a home birth
OL,18,Fwith their second child, but during
OL,19,Flabour Preeti was rushed to Leicester
OL,20,FRoyal Infirmary when concerns were
OL,21,Fraised about her baby's positioning.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1772201047
OL,3,CParents of baby boy who lived two days
OL,4,Csay maternity review must lead to
OL,5,Cchange
OL,7,FThroughout pregnancy, Preeti said her
OL,8,Fbaby consistently measured above the
OL,9,F90th percentile.
OL,11,F"We don't believe a home birth should
OL,12,Fhave been an option. They should have
OL,13,Frecommended a C-section," she said.
OL,15,FThe family said once at hospital there
OL,16,Fwere critical delays, poor
OL,17,Fcommunication and a lack of urgency in
OL,18,Fcarrying out an emergency caesarean
OL,19,Fsection.
OL,26,@sD@AOUuD@YO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1772201047
OL,3,CParents of baby boy who lived two days
OL,4,Csay maternity review must lead to
OL,5,Cchange
OL,7,F"When we went in, there was no sense
OL,8,Fof emergency. The equipment wasn't
OL,9,Fpresent and it took around half an
OL,10,Fhour to locate it."
OL,12,FBy the time Ansh was delivered, the
OL,13,Fcouple say he had been without oxygen
OL,14,Ffor too long. He suffered brain damage
OL,15,Fand died two days later. Preeti also
OL,16,Flost two litres of blood and suffered
OL,17,Fa ruptured uterus.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@SO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1772201047
OL,3,CParents of baby boy who lived two days
OL,4,Csay maternity review must lead to
OL,5,Cchange
OL,7,FUniversity Hospitals of Leicester is
OL,8,Fone of 12 trusts being examined across
OL,9,FEngland, as part of the maternity
OL,10,Freview led by Baroness Valerie Amos.
OL,12,FThe family said many of the concerns
OL,13,Falready highlighted by the review,
OL,14,Fincluding delays and not listening to
OL,15,Fmothers, reflect their experience.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1772201047
OL,3,CParents of baby boy who lived two days
OL,4,Csay maternity review must lead to
OL,5,Cchange
OL,7,FWhile the review promises to produce
OL,8,Fnational recommendations to improve
OL,9,Fstandards of care when it publishes
OL,10,Fits findings in the spring, the couple
OL,11,Fquestion whether it will lead to
OL,12,Fmeaningful change.
OL,14,F"You want someone to check up and say:
OL,15,F'This is what we asked you to make
OL,16,Fchanges on. Have you done that? Can
OL,17,Fyou show it to us? And what have you
OL,18,Fdone about this? And how will this
OL,19,Fpositively impact families in the
OL,20,Ffuture?'"
OL,26,@vD@AOU|D@IO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1772201047
OL,3,CParents of baby boy who lived two days
OL,4,Csay maternity review must lead to
OL,5,Cchange
OL,7,FThe couple fears the findings could
OL,8,Fbecome "bullet points in a report"
OL,9,Frather than a catalyst for reform.
OL,11,F"Otherwise, we'll keep going the same
OL,12,Fway and if that's the case, then a
OL,13,Fpublic inquiry would be the only right
OL,14,Fanswer," said Rishi.
OL,16,FThe couple are taking legal action
OL,17,Fagainst University Hospitals of
OL,18,FLeicester NHS Trust.
OL,26,@pD@HOUpD@bO]sD@AOUvD@HO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1772201047
OL,3,CParents of baby boy who lived two days
OL,4,Csay maternity review must lead to
OL,5,Cchange
OL,7,FJulie Hogg, Chief Nurse at University
OL,8,FHospitals of Leicester NHS Trust,
OL,9,Fsaid: "We offer our deepest apologies
OL,10,Fto Mr and Mrs Joshi for the care they
OL,11,Freceived, and for the circumstances
OL,12,Fthat led to Ansh's death in 2022.
OL,14,F"We have learned from their experience
OL,15,Fand have made important improvements
OL,16,Fto patient safety and the care we
OL,17,Fprovide.
OL,26,@qD@GOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1772201047
OL,3,CParents of baby boy who lived two days
OL,4,Csay maternity review must lead to
OL,5,Cchange
OL,7,F"While we are unable to comment
OL,8,Ffurther at this stage due to ongoing
OL,9,Flegal proceedings, our thoughts and
OL,10,Fcondolences are with them and their
OL,11,Ffamily."
OL,13,FAs the national review examines what
OL,14,Fwent wrong, and what must change, for
OL,15,FAnsh's parents this is no longer about
OL,16,Ftheir own loss but ensuring maternity
OL,17,Fservices are safe for every family.
OL,19,F"In this day and age we can do better.
OL,20,FAnd we should be doing better," Preeti
OL,21,Fsaid.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
